Kaeon Waypoint

	Philosophy

		-
			All of the state and data management utilities within the Kaeon APIs shall collectively
			be known as Kaeon Waypoint.
		-

	Principles

		Conventions

			Action ACE

				-
					Kaeon Waypoint shall primarily be designed around action ACE.
				-

			Value Monitors

				-
					Kaeon Waypoint shall make use of value monitors to allow subscriptions and
					entanglement with and across databases.
				-

		APIs

			Waypoint Core